{"tid":1309111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝一路為呢個香港默默付出嘅你哋","createTime":"2019-07-12T05:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T14:58:08.000Z","uid":165869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa5a2beb8121d828a7bc7210d0447f7a2a4a2253","tid":1309111,"uid":165869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:34:45.000Z","msg":"反送中運動從69、612開始持續至今已經一個月，長期嘅抗爭都令大家感覺到疲倦。<br />\n或者你開始感覺到無力、沮喪，但喺呢到我衷心嘅同各位講一聲，多謝。<br />\n多謝你哋能夠堅持至今，每個人都各司其職，用自己嘅方法改變呢個仍有希望嘅香港。<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得攰，我希望你能夠休息兩日，然後繼續堅持抗爭。<br />\n如果你打算放棄，我想請你睇下繼續努力緊嘅各位，你真係捨得放棄呢個屋企？<br />\n<br />\n我唔會講咩大道理，我都唔知道可以講咩鼓勵咁多位，所以我只係想借呢個post多謝寂寂無聞嘅咁多位同路人。<br />\n<br />\n多謝為香港企出嚟嘅咁多位，多謝喺前線義無反顧地抗爭嘅你哋、多謝支援、掩護前線嘅咁多位手足，勇武同和理非係香港嘅矛同盾，係抗爭路上嘅齒同唇，多謝你哋嘅挺身而出，多謝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6E2rm7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6E2rm7U.jpg&h=8bdb05b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yAtmVsV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyAtmVsV.jpg&h=23fd2219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2RfZVa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2RfZVa.jpg&h=2fe0f53c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝一班真正為香港勞心勞力嘅議員，不論喺立法會內、定係喺前線上嘅你哋，多謝你哋保護屬於香港人嘅寶貴自由、保護喺前線勇武抗爭嘅義士，減少佢哋受傷嘅機會，多謝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKdYXL0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKdYXL0.jpg&h=bf575251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQyVfxE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQyVfxE.jpg&h=05dfc11b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTz5CEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTz5CEQ.jpg&h=2d233bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MA4M6wN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMA4M6wN.jpg&h=042dae73&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝用唔同形式為香港奮鬥嘅你哋：登報、連儂牆、抵制、課金、報道......唔好覺得你哋做嘅嘢係冇用同無謂，或者堅持未必會有答案，但放棄就一定代表滅亡，多謝你哋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PiLAfxp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPiLAfxp.png&h=9f331fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fSHVZY8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfSHVZY8.png&h=68f75ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ySZHcu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ySZHcu.jpg&h=07626186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQuUv5Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQuUv5Q.png&h=11a80318&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S61zv6o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS61zv6o.jpg&h=95fee6e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTd6ng1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTd6ng1.jpg&h=46efaddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭路上，總有人加入、有人離場。加入嘅人為香港而努力，離開嘅人因香港而活著。唔知道你哋仲記唔記得佢哋？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/12/131332_c682e5c850eb331f7f741361e6b119ac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F12%2F131332_c682e5c850eb331f7f741361e6b119ac.png&h=27653a31&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zaTMFP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zaTMFP.png&h=8ee9c38a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bb6vOUa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbb6vOUa.png&h=8d896b32&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n對唔住，因為我哋仲未成功爭取到。<br />\n多謝，因為你哋令香港人團結同醒覺。<br />\n<br />\n大家都發過夢、遊行過；<br />\n請大家繼續堅持，繼續努力；<br />\n我相信多多少少都會覺得攰，但為咗香港，呢一切都係值得嘅。<br />\n<br />\n我哋係香港人，我哋熱愛香港。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BUOewaG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBUOewaG.jpg&h=fe6dd1ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭仲未完結，為堅持嘅各位、為死去嘅佢哋、為你自己、為屬於大家嘅香港，繼續努力。要多謝嘅人太多，我都講唔曬，喺最後嘅呢到，我想同各位講多次，多謝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxZAZ4s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxZAZ4s.png&h=cd4d8933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你有想多謝嘅人同事，請你喺下面繼續分享。<br />\n如果你有不滿想發洩，入嚟呢到屌我，向我宣洩，但發洩完請繼續為香港奮鬥。<br />\n我願意做你哋嘅垃圾桶、雖然我俾唔到希望你哋，但我能夠承擔你哋嘅絕望。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/LeeShanYin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FLeeShanYin&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUykPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=3ea48fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/LeeShanYin</a><br />\n<br />\n多謝睇完嘅各位，如果可以，請鼓勵身邊嘅咁多位同伴，我哋會一直企喺佢哋背後同隔嚟。"},{"pid":"17a94437a3ef6738f504676bd88fcde760c5722c","tid":1309111,"uid":126280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:38:20.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n<br />\nwe are hong konger！"},{"pid":"eb22f2ed6bbda42d0d3069c725258b9603d5afc0","tid":1309111,"uid":165869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"相嗌唔好口 欣賞下同路人 <br />\n自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}